<p>Thereâ€™s only <strong>Bold</strong> or <em>Italic</em> to emphasize text. Of course thereâ€™s <strong><em>Bold and Italic</em></strong>. I donâ€™t want to highlight text with some containers like blockquote. I wondered what can I do. And there was</p>

<pre><code class="language-emphasis">"CODE BLOCK"
